title: Elbeyli, Mut
summary: Elbeyli is a village in Mut district of Mersin Province, Turkey. It is situated to the west of Turkish state highway  D.715. The distance to Mut is 4 kilometres (2.5 mi) and to Mersin is 158 kilometres (98 mi). The population of the village was 438 as of 2012.
